(190, 1, '2017-01-25 16:52:11', '2017-01-25 19:52:11', '<div class=\"container\">\\r\\n	<div class=\"row\">\\r\\n		<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12\">\\r\\n			<div class=\"subtitles single-header\">\\r\\n			    <h1 class=\"paragraph\">Baterias</h1>							\\r\\n			</div>							\\r\\n		</div>\\r\\n	</div>\\r\\n</div>\\r\\n<div class=\"wrapper-slider\">\\r\\n			<div class=\"pattern\"></div>\\r\\n			<div class=\"header\">\\r\\n				<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/datawaves/images/header-baterias.jpg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\" alt=\"\">\\r\\n			</div>\\r\\n		</div>\\r\\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\\r\\n<div class=\"container\">\\r\\n		<div class=\"row\">\\r\\n			<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12\">\\r\\n				<h2 class=\"title-internal\">Amplia gama de baterías, generadores de hidrógeno y accesorios.</h2>\\r\\n				<div class=\"line-short\"></div>\\r\\n				<p class=\"paragraph-internal\">Somos, desde 2009, distribuidores oficiales en Argentina de los <strong>sistemas de almacenamiento de energía NARADA</strong>, líder mundial en soluciones de almacenamiento de energía para aplicaciones industriales.</p>\\r\\n				<p class=\"paragraph-internal\">De esa forma, ofrecemos al mercado una muy amplia familia de baterías con <strong>tecnología de electrolito absorbido y gel</strong>, las cuales brindan un elevado rendimiento.</p>\\r\\n			</div>\\r\\n		</div>\\r\\n	</div>			\\r\\n	<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\\r\\n	<div class=\"container\">\\r\\n		<div class=\"row\">\\r\\n			<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12\">\\r\\n				<h2 class=\"title-internal\">Los productos NARADA nos permiten ofrecer la más alta calidad</h2>\\r\\n				<div class=\"line-short\"></div>\\r\\n			</div>\\r\\n		</div>\\r\\n	</div>\\r\\n	<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\\r\\n	<div class=\"container\">\\r\\n		<div class=\"row boxes-green\">\\r\\n			<div class=\"col-xs-6 col-md-3 col-lg-3 mb-10\">\\r\\n				<div class=\"bg-green height-230\">\\r\\n					<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/datawaves/images/baterias/icn-baterias-01.png\" alt=\"\">					\\r\\n					<h3 class=\"title-internal uppercase\">Excelente capacidad de carga</h3>\\r\\n				</div>\\r\\n			</div>\\r\\n			<div class=\"col-xs-6 col-md-3 col-lg-3 mb-10\">					\\r\\n				<div class=\"bg-green height-230\">\\r\\n					<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/datawaves/images/baterias/icn-baterias-02.png\" alt=\"\">				\\r\\n					<h3 class=\"title-internal uppercase\">Baja capacidad de auto-descarga</h3>\\r\\n					<p>Menor a 2% mensual, 25ºC </p>\\r\\n				</div>\\r\\n			</div>\\r\\n			<div class=\"col-xs-6 col-md-3 col-lg-3 mb-10\">					\\r\\n				<div class=\"bg-green height-230\">\\r\\n					<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/datawaves/images/baterias/icn-baterias-03.png\" alt=\"\">					\\r\\n					<h3 class=\"title-internal uppercase\">Sistema regulado por válvula</h3>\\r\\n					<p>Sin adición de agua</p>\\r\\n				</div>\\r\\n			</div>\\r\\n			<div class=\"col-xs-6 col-md-3 col-lg-3 mb-10\">					\\r\\n				<div class=\"bg-green height-230\">\\r\\n					<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/datawaves/images/baterias/icn-baterias-04.png\" alt=\"\">					\\r\\n					<h3 class=\"title-internal uppercase\">Variadas formas de instalación</h3>\\r\\n				</div>\\r\\n			</div>\\r\\n			<div class=\"col-xs-6 col-md-3 col-lg-3 mb-10\">					\\r\\n				<div class=\"bg-green height-230\">\\r\\n					<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/datawaves/images/baterias/icn-baterias-05.png\" alt=\"\">					\\r\\n					<h3 class=\"title-internal uppercase\">normativas internacionales</h3>\\r\\n				</div>\\r\\n			</div>\\r\\n			<div class=\"col-xs-6 col-md-3 col-lg-3 mb-10\">					\\r\\n				<div class=\"bg-green height-230\">\\r\\n					<img src=\"http://localhost:8888/datawaves/images/baterias/icn-baterias-06.png\" alt=\"\">						\\r\\n					<h3 class=\"title-internal uppercase\">temperaturas extremas</h3>\\r\\n					<p>Alta performance</p>\\r\\n				</div>\\r\\n			</div>\\r\\n			<div class=\"col-xs-6 col-md-3 col-lg-3 mb-10\">					\\r\\n				<div cl